* {{a|US}} {{IPA|en|/əˈpɹuvəl/}}
* {{audio|en|en-us-approval.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# An expression granting [[permission]]; an indication of [[agreement]] with a [[proposal]]; an [[acknowledgement]] that a person, thing{{,}} or event [[meet]]s [[requirement]]s.
#: {{ux|en|I need to get an '''approval''' on this purchase order.}}
# An expression of favorable [[acceptance]] and [[encouragement]]; a [[compliment]] that also [[condone]]s.
#: {{ux|en|Words of '''approval''' never seem to come from him.}}
# {{lb|en|especially|philately}} Something [[mail]]ed by a [[seller]] to a [[collector]] to match their [[state]]d [[interest]]s; the collector can [[approve]] of or [[return]] the item.

